    <description><![CDATA[<h1>全局监听器</h1>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 全局监听器可以监听整个系统的动作的执行，如XWorker的调试功能，以及动作性能记录等都是通过全局监听器实现的。</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 要添加一个全局监听器可以通过World对象。</p>

<pre class="brush:groovy;">
import org.xmeta.Thing;
import org.xmeta.World;

World world = World.getInstance();

//添加全局监听器
world.addGlobalActionListener(Thing listener);

//移除全局监听器
world.removeGlobalActionListener(Thing listener);</pre>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></description>
    <en_description><![CDATA[<h1>Global ActionListener</h1>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; The global listener can monitor the execution of the whole system, such as the debugging function of xworker, and the action performance record are all realized through the global listener.</p>

<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; To add a global listener, you can pass through the world object.</p>

<pre class="brush:groovy;">
import org.xmeta.Thing;
import org.xmeta.World;

World world = World.getInstance();

//Add global action listener
world.addGlobalActionListener(Thing listener);

//Remvoe global action listener
world.removeGlobalActionListener(Thing listener);</pre>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
]]></en_description>
</QuickContent>